---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The Forge — Grithos Chapters"
  description="The Forge is the Grithos chapter model. A builder's table where real problems get solved by real people. No vulnerability theater. No lectures. Just builders building."
  activePage="the-forge"
>

<section class="forge-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero-content reveal">
      <p class="section-overline">Grithos Chapters</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">The Forge</h1>
      <div class="hero-line"></div>
      <p class="hero-sub">A builder's table. You bring your work, the room makes it better, and you leave with one thing to do before next time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="gold-divider" />

<section class="forge-what">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="what-grid">
      <div class="what-text reveal">
        <p class="section-overline">What It Is</p>
        <h2>Not a meeting.<br/>Not a support group.<br/>A war room.</h2>
        <p>Think startup pitch night meets Masonic lodge. Every person at the table is building something. Every person leaves with something they didn't have walking in.</p>
        <p>No vulnerability theater. No shared suffering. No lectures about mindset. You share what you're building, not what you're struggling with.</p>
        <p>Whiteboard. Markers. Index cards. One tenet. That's it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="what-stats reveal d2">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">90</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Minutes. Hard stop.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">3</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Minutes per person on the whiteboard</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">1</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Commitment you walk out with</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">0</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Certifications needed to lead one</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="gold-divider" />

<section class="forge-format">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="section-overline reveal">The Format</p>
    <h2 class="sec-title reveal d1">The Builder's Table</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub reveal d2">90 minutes. Weekly or biweekly. Six segments. Zero filler.</p>

    <div class="format-timeline">

      <div class="format-block reveal">
        <div class="format-time">
          <span class="time-range">0:00 – 0:05</span>
        </div>
        <div class="format-content">
          <h3>The Open</h3>
          <p>Chapter leader reads one tenet. No preamble, no welcome speech. Just the words. Then:</p>
          <blockquote>"What are you building? Let's go."</blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="format-block reveal">
        <div class="format-time">
          <span class="time-range">0:05 – 0:30</span>
        </div>
        <div class="format-content">
          <h3>The Board</h3>
          <p>Whiteboard up front. Each person gets 3 minutes max:</p>
          <ol>
            <li>Write what you're building this week</li>
            <li>State your one blocker</li>
            <li>Room responds — solutions only, no questions about feelings</li>
          </ol>
          <div class="example-exchange">
            <p class="example"><em>"I'm launching a pressure washing site. Blocker: can't figure out pricing."</em></p>
            <p class="example response"><em>"Charge $150 minimum, $0.15/sq ft above that. Next."</em></p>
          </div>
          <p>Fast. Direct. Useful. If someone doesn't have a blocker, they share what's working so others can steal the playbook. Nobody leaves without giving or getting something concrete.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="format-block reveal">
        <div class="format-time">
          <span class="time-range">0:30 – 0:45</span>
        </div>
        <div class="format-content">
          <h3>The Tenet</h3>
          <p>Chapter leader connects this week's tenet to building. Not a philosophy class — a <strong>case study</strong>. Real person, real decision, real outcome.</p>
          <blockquote>"Tenet III: BUILD SOMETHING THAT OUTLASTS YOU. Here's a guy who built a $2M landscaping company in 3 years starting with a borrowed mower. He's 28. His dad mowed lawns his whole life and died with nothing. Same work, different intent. One was a job, one was a legacy. What are you building — a job or a legacy?"</blockquote>
          <p>5-minute discussion. Not deep sharing — sharp takes. Agree, disagree, move.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="format-block featured reveal">
        <div class="format-time">
          <span class="time-range">0:45 – 1:05</span>
        </div>
        <div class="format-content">
          <h3>The Workshop</h3>
          <p class="hook-text">This is where Grithos separates from everything else.</p>
          <p>Pick ONE person's blocker from The Board and the whole room attacks it together for 20 minutes. Collectively solve a real problem for a real person, right now, in the room.</p>
          <p>One week it's someone's business plan. Next week it's someone's resume. Next week it's someone figuring out how to have a hard conversation with a business partner. The room builds the solution together — on the whiteboard, in real time.</p>
          <p class="hook-text">Everyone leaves having watched a problem get solved. That's addictive. That's why they come back.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="format-block reveal">
        <div class="format-time">
          <span class="time-range">1:05 – 1:15</span>
        </div>
        <div class="format-content">
          <h3>The Commitment</h3>
          <p>No going around the room. No spotlight. Everyone writes ONE action on an index card. Specific. Measurable. Due by next meeting.</p>
          <div class="commitment-examples">
            <span class="card">"Call 10 prospects by Friday."</span>
            <span class="card">"File the LLC paperwork Tuesday."</span>
            <span class="card">"Have the conversation with my co-founder before Thursday."</span>
          </div>
          <p>Hand it to the person next to you. They'll ask you next week. Not the leader — your peer. <strong>Horizontal accountability, not top-down.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="format-block reveal">
        <div class="format-time">
          <span class="time-range">1:15 – 1:20</span>
        </div>
        <div class="format-content">
          <h3>The Close</h3>
          <blockquote>"Nobody in this room is here because they're lost. You're here because you're building. Go build."</blockquote>
          <p>Done. Clean exit. No one's obligated to stay. If people grab food or drinks after, it happens naturally — but the meeting has a hard stop.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="gold-divider" />

<section class="forge-why">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="section-overline reveal">Why It Works</p>
    <h2 class="sec-title reveal d1">The Unfair Advantage</h2>

    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-card reveal">
        <div class="why-icon">◼</div>
        <h3>No Vulnerability Theater</h3>
        <p>You share what you're building, not what you're struggling with. The energy is forward, not backward.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card reveal d1">
        <div class="why-icon">◼</div>
        <h3>Immediate Value</h3>
        <p>Every person leaves with at least one solution they didn't have walking in. Not inspiration — an answer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card reveal d2">
        <div class="why-icon">◼</div>
        <h3>The Workshop Is the Hook</h3>
        <p>Watching a room of builders attack your problem is something you can't get from a podcast or a book. It's the thing that brings people back.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card reveal d3">
        <div class="why-icon">◼</div>
        <h3>15 Tenets = 15 Weeks</h3>
        <p>Five Pillars. Three tenets each. Content doesn't repeat for nearly four months. By then the room is different people with different builds. It stays fresh.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card reveal d4">
        <div class="why-icon">◼</div>
        <h3>Scales With a Playbook</h3>
        <p>Any builder can run this format. No special training, no certification. Whiteboard, markers, index cards, one tenet. That's the entire toolkit.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card reveal d5">
        <div class="why-icon">◼</div>
        <h3>Horizontal Accountability</h3>
        <p>Your peer holds your commitment card, not a leader. You answer to someone building alongside you, not above you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="gold-divider" />

<section class="forge-first">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="first-content reveal">
      <p class="section-overline">Chapter One</p>
      <h2 class="sec-title">Slidell, Louisiana</h2>
      <p class="first-text">The first Grithos chapter launches in Slidell, LA — April 2026. One table, one whiteboard, whoever shows up ready to build.</p>
      <p class="first-text">This isn't a franchise model. It's a format. If you want to run one in your city, you take the playbook and you run it. No permission needed. No fees. Just builders building.</p>
      <div class="first-cta">
        <a href="/practice" class="btn btn-primary">Get the Daily Practice →</a>
        <a href="/footing" class="btn btn-ghost">Start Here</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* ═══ HERO ═══ */
.forge-hero {
  padding: 140px 0 80px;
  text-align: center;
}
.hero-content {
  max-width: 720px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.hero-title {
  font-family: var(--heading);
  font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 80px);
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.hero-line {
  width: 80px;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--gold);
  margin: 0 auto 24px;
}
.hero-sub {
  font-size: 18px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

/* ═══ WHAT IT IS ═══ */
.forge-what {
  padding: 80px 0;
}
.what-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 60px;
  align-items: center;
}
.what-text h2 {
  font-family: var(--heading);
  font-size: clamp(26px, 3.5vw, 38px);
  line-height: 1.2;
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  border: none;
  display: block;
  padding: 0;
}
.what-text p {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.what-stats {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 20px;
}
.stat-card {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--r-lg);
  padding: 28px 24px;
  text-align: center;
  transition: border-color .3s;
}
.stat-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--gold-border);
}
.stat-number {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--heading);
  font-size: 48px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.stat-label {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.4;
}

/* ═══ FORMAT / TIMELINE ═══ */
.forge-format {
  padding: 80px 0;
}
.format-timeline {
  margin-top: 40px;
}
.format-block {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
  gap: 32px;
  padding: 40px 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.format-block:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}
.format-block.featured {
  background: var(--gold-soft);
  border: 1px solid var(--gold-border);
  border-radius: var(--r-lg);
  padding: 40px 32px;
  margin: 20px 0;
}
.format-time {
  text-align: right;
  padding-top: 4px;
}
.time-range {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--gold);
  letter-spacing: .02em;
}
.format-content h3 {
  font-family: var(--heading);
  font-size: 24px;
  color: var(--gold);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.format-content p {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.format-content ol {
  margin: 12px 0 16px 20px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.8;
}
.format-content blockquote {
  border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
  padding: 12px 20px;
  margin: 16px 0;
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 17px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.hook-text {
  color: var(--white) !important;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 17px;
}

/* Example exchange */
.example-exchange {
  background: var(--card);
  border-radius: var(--r);
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 16px 0;
}
.example {
  color: var(--text-secondary) !important;
  margin-bottom: 8px !important;
}
.example.response {
  color: var(--gold-light) !important;
  margin-bottom: 0 !important;
}

/* Commitment cards */
.commitment-examples {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 12px;
  margin: 16px 0;
}
.card {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--r);
  padding: 10px 16px;
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 14px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--text);
}

/* ═══ WHY IT WORKS ═══ */
.forge-why {
  padding: 80px 0;
}
.why-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
  margin-top: 40px;
}
.why-card {
  background: var(--card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--r-lg);
  padding: 32px 28px;
  transition: border-color .3s, transform .3s;
}
.why-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--gold-border);
  transform: translateY(-4px);
}
.why-icon {
  color: var(--gold);
  font-size: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.why-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--heading);
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.why-card p {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ═══ FIRST CHAPTER ═══ */
.forge-first {
  padding: 80px 0 100px;
  text-align: center;
}
.first-content {
  max-width: 640px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.first-text {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  font-size: 17px;
}
.first-cta {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: 32px;
}

/* ═══ RESPONSIVE ═══ */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .what-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  .format-block {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .format-block.featured {
    padding: 28px 20px;
  }
  .format-time {
    text-align: left;
  }
  .why-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .commitment-examples {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .first-cta {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
}
</style>
</BaseLayout>
